ized Version of the New Testament, and in most modern European languages. This was the name of the mother of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Careless was born in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Surnud","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Kuollut","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Décédée","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Careless est née à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Verstorben","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Careless wurde in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Desede","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"elhunyt","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Anglia, United Kingdom"},"id":{"–":"Telah Meninggal","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Telah Meninggal","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Inggris, United Kingdom"},"it":{"–":"Deceduta","1580–1680":"1580–1680","–Female":"Deceduta","1680":"1680","1580":"1580","Eng.":"Inghilterra, Regno Unito","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Careless è nata il nel Inghilterra, Regno Unito. Lei avuto almeno 1 figlio."},"ja":{"–":"死亡","1580–1680":"1580年–1680年","–Female":"死亡","1680":"1680年","1580":"1580年","Eng.":"イギリスイギリス","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Carelessはイギリス